Mefs hidden repo:

$ su
Password:
# vim /usr/pkg/etc/pkgin/repositories.conf

Now change the URL from whatever you have right now to
http://www.ki.nu/pkgsrc/packages/current/.9.0/All/
and save the file.
This is the hidden repo!

# pkgin update
# pkgin full-upgrade
# pkgin autoremove
# pkgin clean
# exit
$

Keep it in sync with pkgsrc and keep an eye on the bulk-builds mailing lists. Check the mailing lists before you do updates/upgrades to be sure that you don't break your packages.
